OL,3,CHow much will your council tax go up
OL,4,Cin Wales?
OL,6,FCouncils across Wales have voted on
OL,7,Ftheir budgets for 2024-25, including
OL,8,Fmuch council tax will increase.
OL,10,FThe amount by which council tax has
OL,11,Fincreased varies across the different
OL,12,Fcouncils in Wales with an increase of
OL,13,F4.95% in Torfaen, while Pembrokeshire
OL,14,Fhas seen the highest increase at 12.5%.
OL,16,FThese hikes come as the Welsh Local
OL,17,FGovernment Association (WLGA) says
OL,18,Fcouncils face a #432 million shortfall
OL,19,Fafter council tax rises.
