OL,3,CHow much will your council tax go up
OL,4,Cin Wales?
OL,6,FCouncil tax is money you pay to your
OL,7,Flocal council and is based on the
OL,8,Fvalue of your home.
OL,10,FIt pays for services your local
OL,11,Fcouncil provides including bin
OL,12,Fcollections, road maintenance, and
OL,13,Frunning local schools.
OL,15,FAround 20% of council revenue spend is
OL,16,Fgenerated from council tax but it
OL,17,Fvaries between each local authority.
OL,19,FHow much will your council tax bill go
OL,20,Fup?
