OL,3,CHow much will your council tax go up
OL,4,Cin Wales?
OL,6,FWho is exempt from paying council tax?
OL,8,FNot everyone has to pay council tax.
OL,9,FThere may also be circumstances where
OL,10,Fyour bill may be reduced.
OL,12,FYou are exempt from paying council tax
OL,13,Fif all of those living in the property
OL,14,Fare full-time university or college
OL,15,Fstudents or all of the residents are
OL,16,Funder 18.
OL,18,FSince the 1 April 2019, care leavers
OL,19,Funder the age of 25 have been exempt
OL,20,Ffrom paying council tax in all areas
OL,21,Fof Wales.
